    <item>
      <title>最高法院裁决后，特朗普再次威胁解雇美联储理事丽莎·库克</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/29/us/politics/trump-fire-fed-governor-cook.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统承诺对他试图解雇的美联储理事丽莎·库克“立即采取适当行动”，尽管法院确认美联储官员只能因故被解雇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/29/us/politics/trump-fire-fed-governor-cook.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 22:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
